# Skillfile (github.com/eljulians/skillfile)
# Skill sources live in skills/. The Claude Code deploy (.claude/skills/) is
# committed so the skill works on a fresh clone without running any tooling.
# The other tools' deploy targets and the downloaded CLI binary are regenerated
# on demand by `make skills-install`, so they are not committed.
.codex/skills/
.github/skills/
.skillfile/cache/
.skillfile/conflict
bin/skillfile
